videos.description: Wyoming QB Nick Smith has his pass tipped and intercepted by Dakari Monroe who returns it back 33 yards all the way down to the Wyoming 22-yard line.
videos.headline: Spartans force INT, return it deep into Cowboys' territory

videos.description: Spartans QB Montel Aaron scores on an option  keeper from 5 yards out to give San Jose State an early 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: Aaron beats defenders to pylon for San Jose State TD

videos.description: San Jose State QB Montel Aaron goes deep, but has his pass intercepted by Marcus Epps who returns it back 57 yards the other way.
videos.headline: Cowboys' Epps picks off pass at the goal line

videos.description: San Jose State QB Montel Aaron lofts a pass downfield to Tre Hartley who leaps above the defender to haul in the pass for a 37-yard pickup.
videos.headline: Spartans air it out for big gain

videos.description: Nick Smith keeps it himself at the goal line and scores on a QB sneak from a yard out.
videos.headline: Smith sneaks it in for Wyoming TD

videos.description: San Jose State CB Dakari Monroe picks off Nick Smith's pass in the red zone to record his second interception of the game.
videos.headline: Spartans' Monroe gets second INT of first half

videos.description: Cowboys RB Kellen Overstreet takes a handoff and breaks free, evading defenders on his way to a 33-yard gain, setting up a Wyoming field goal.
videos.headline: Overstreet jukes defender to put Wyoming in red zone

videos.description: San Jose State's Andre Chachere is thrown out of the game for delivering a punishing blow to the helmet of a Wyoming receiver.
videos.headline: Spartans' Chachere ejected for targeting

videos.description: Trailing by 10 late,  Cowboys QB Nick Smith connects with C.J. Johnson who jukes a defender and scores from 53 yards out.
videos.headline: Wyoming's Johnson takes it to the house

videos.description: Jay Taylor and Wayne Randazzo break down the Spartans' surprise 20-17 victory against the Cowboys, citing San Jose State's stout defense as the key to the win.
videos.headline: San Jose State upsets Wyoming
